{"tid":1847993,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"夾公仔機變夾口罩機！（圖）","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:32:40.000Z","uid":216662,"like":50,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a435546fcf33a79eee2f1579b7a94d41adbd4f16","tid":1847993,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLWTN2j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLWTN2j.jpg&h=a01ccff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4ggLO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4ggLO1.jpg&h=a7275bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多人入錢，未見到人夾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c647e922cda61fddd1eec7f06b1370964973195f","tid":1847993,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=1f0e2d26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=9e5baf56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2